#API-UI-Tests-Template

This repository provides a template for setting up automated API and UI tests for TeamCity using Docker, Playwright, and Pytest.

## **Table of Contents**
- **[Overview](#overview)**
- **[Project Structure](#project-structure)**
- **[Setup](#setup)**
- **[Running the Automation](#running-the-automation)**
